; Coverage test for post.cc get_price (L241-248), get_commodity (L206-217),
; and get_commodity_is_primary (L219-224).
; Tests price with annotation (L244-245) and without (L246-247).
; Tests commodity and primary on different posting types.

2024/01/01 Stock Purchase
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Simple Purchase
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(price)|%(commodity)|%(primary)|%(account)\n"
$1500.00|AAPL|false|Assets:Brokerage
$-1500.00|$|true|Assets:Cash
$10.00|$|true|Expenses:Food
$-10.00|$|true|Assets:Cash
end test
